{"id": "1512488029544120379", "channel_id": "1512069671552290939", "type": 0, "author_id": "434629255180320769", "author_name": "kam03212000", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為看到你說混池 以為是千冪那種大雜池", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T16:07:26.912000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1512069671552290939", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人求各種幫忙", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1512488132803821732", "channel_id": "1512069671552290939", "type": 19, "author_id": "434629255180320769", "author_name": "kam03212000", "author_bot": false, "content": "畢竟明天還送150+150  所以還好？<:chicken_a08:917813080912707635>", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T16:07:51.531000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["400656449417773066"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1512487589339332648", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1512069671552290939", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人求各種幫忙", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1512489121719914698", "channel_id": "1512069671552290939", "type": 0, "author_id": "434629255180320769", "author_name": "kam03212000", "author_bot": false, "content": "那我現在開始忍著等茉夏的池再抽看看 然後再找大大們檢驗一下要不要全抽茉夏\n\n感謝大大", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T16:11:47.307000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-05T16:15:25.911000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1512069671552290939", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人求各種幫忙", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1512491619017035796", "channel_id": "1512069671552290939", "type": 19, "author_id": "400656449417773066", "author_name": "cpu7954", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為你現在其實光靠原型就夠補茉夏到超限了\n融災向的話我覺得也可以考慮抽誕墨", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T16:21:42.709000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["434629255180320769"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1512489121719914698", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1512069671552290939", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人求各種幫忙", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1512495076146806854", "channel_id": "1512069671552290939", "type": 0, "author_id": "434629255180320769", "author_name": "kam03212000", "author_bot": false, "content": "其實我在找角色資源是有看到好幾個很強的角色 \n只是要不根本本體也沒抽到 要不就是只有一個 ，茉夏也是剛好群星抽中了一個才會比較高星數 \n\n因為單純沙耶入坑，所以在配隊上完全一竅不通，當初開帖找大大們配隊看到自己包包東缺西缺，也是擔心會不會錢都掉大海了<:848549167802613790:873892919977852958>", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T16:35:26.953000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1512069671552290939", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人求各種幫忙", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1512499116586958869", "channel_id": "1512069671552290939", "type": 0, "author_id": "434629255180320769", "author_name": "kam03212000", "author_bot": false, "content": "最頭痛大概是明知道不應該每樣都抽一點點 要集中把基本盤抽出來也好  \n\n我還是有點手癢會抽千冪（剛剛又來了30  又多了一個阿拉😂）\n\n其實本來最想玩的是深海/超維\n可惜這兩邊最核心的好像也沒齊/沒到最低標準", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T16:51:30.269000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1512069671552290939", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人求各種幫忙", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
